title: Fathom - Kiani Vol. 2 (2012) (Digital) (K6-Empire)
description:
Fathom: Kiani Vol. 2

English | CBR | 5 Issues

Genre: Action/Adventure, Fantasy, Science Fiction

Written by Vince Hernandez
Art by Oliver Nome

Collects Fathom: Kiani Volume 2 #0-4.

This all-new Fathom saga kicks off with the return of one of the Aspen Universe's favorite heroines, Kiani, as she returns to the awe-inspiring underwater world of the Blue seeking vengeance for her past! The neutral truce between the Humans and the Blue has taken an emotional toll on the inhabitants under the surface-and their future as a unified body remains uncertain. Now, all bets are off as Kiani's true power and capabilities-as well as shocking secrets from the past are revealed!
